--input-shadow.light: inset 0 0 0 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 12%), 0 2px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 5%), 0 1px 1.5px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 3%), 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 4%), 0 0 0 0 transparent

--input-shadow-hover.light: inset 0 0 0 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 17%), 0 2px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 10%), 0 1px 1.5px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 3%), 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 4%), 0 0 0 0 transparent

.theme-light.value: inset 0 0 0 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 12%), 0 2px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 5%), 0 1px 1.5px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 3%), 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 4%), 0 0 0 0 transparent
inset 0 0 0 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 17%), 0 2px 3px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 10%), 0 1px 1.5px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 3%), 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(0 0 0 / 4%), 0 0 0 0 transparent

.mod-rtl.value: linear-gradient( to right, transparent var(--size-4-6), black var(--size-4-6) )

.checkbox-container:after.value: transform 0.15s ease-in-out, width 0.1s ease-in-out, left 0.1s ease-in-out

.theme-dark .pdf-container.mod-themed .p.value: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px var(--color-base-60)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))

.popupWrapper > div.value: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3))

.canvas-color-picker-item.canvas-color-p.value: conic-gradient( var(--color-red), var(--color-yellow), var(--color-green), var(--color-blue), var(--color-purple), var(--color-red) )

.mobile-navbar-text.value: linear-gradient( to left, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) var(--size-4-4), #000000 var(--size-4-8) )

.ulu-grad .workspace::before.value: radial-gradient( circle, var(--background-secondary) 0%, var(--color-accent) 8.1%, var(--background-secondary) 15.5%, var(--background-secondary) 58.8%, var(--background-secondary) 84.5%, var(--background-secondary) 91.9%, var(--background-secondary) 100% )
